== Introduction ==

This page provides a list of translatable applications in the Ubuntu LiveCd and thus in the default installation. These should be considered higher priority translations, as a subset of the complete list of applications in the `main` presented in the general Ubuntu translation templates page in Launchpad.

Note that this list might vary as we approach Beta and the Release Candidate, where it should be considered stable. Also note that command line applications have been deliberately left out from the list, in order to provide focus to the GUI translations.

== List of translatable applications in the default install ==

* Current development release: Ubuntu 14.04 (Trusty Tahr)
* Simply click on a link in the table to go to that translation in Launchpad and start translating
